summary: [SPOILERS] What should Littlefinger's house words be?
title: [SPOILERS] What should Littlefinger's house words be?
body:
I know he’s gone, but still, I wonder, what should Littlefinger’s house words have been? I know He gave himself the mockingbird* as his sigil, due to him always being so busy with schemes. My brother has proffered “House Baelish: None so devious.” Seems appropriate! Of course, “Chaos is a ladder” would also have to be in contention. What would Baelish have given his own house for house words? What would outsiders have given? What would you give? Personally, I like “started from the bottom now we’re here!” or something along those lines.

*Edited for correction



Source: https://ift.tt/2vCRFJi
